title: Mushroom 11 (v1.02) (GOG)
description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mushroom 11    
https://www.gog.com/game/mushroom_11
Source: GOG.com
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~



About the game: 
================
About: Mold an amorphous organism into any shape by pruning its cells. New cells will immediately grow, allowing you to traverse a mysterious world across brain-twisting obstacles, overcome swarms of bizarre mutated creatures, and understand the true nature of the devastation from which you emerged.


Features:
==========
Mold breaking game about destruction and growth!
7 Chapters each with a changing enviorment!
Music by The Future Sound of London


Version:
=========
Game version 1.02 from October 21, 2015.


Version changes:
=================    


Instructions:
==============
1. Run Setup and Install
2. Play - Enjoy - Seed
 

System Requirements:
=====================
OS: XP / Vista / 7 / 8 / 10
CPU: Single core (Dual-core recommended)
GPU: 256 MB of VRAM 
RAM: 2 GB 
HDD: 500 MB



~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
       Remember to support quality games. If you enjoyed this game - buy it.
